<p dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.7999999999999998; text-align: justify; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;"><span style="font-size: 13.999999999999998pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman',serif; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">+ Lý do khác: mọi chi phí vận chuyển do khách hàng chi trả.</span></p>
